{"tid":288290,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《三五成群》重映 神仙B到場","createTime":"2017-06-18T05:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T20:34:33.000Z","uid":41453,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5414d5445eae025b8ec32644c984452c794037","tid":288290,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"張豪龍、余家豪和蔡堅成出席「903格最港產電影節」，齊齊欣賞18年前由他們主演的作品《三五成群》，眾人笑指勾起很多回憶。在片中演「黑仔」的張豪龍，表示當年大家都未滿18歲，但電影列為三級片，故當年演出後沒有在戲院看過。<br />\n<br />\n「蕃薯」余家豪稱當年翻版碟盛行，知道《三》片是連續兩年翻版冠軍，又說電影改編真實案件，他印象最深刻是燒屍的場口。蔡堅成在片中演「神仙B」一角，他指大家當年演技幼嫩，但合作得很愉快。問到他們可有機會再一起合作？張豪龍笑說：「我們現在收好貴！」余家豪笑謂一切隨緣，大家講心不講金，自言是自掏腰包買飛入場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170610/_2017061018573836969.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170610%2F_2017061018573836969.jpg&h=dd5edf0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170610/photo/bkn-20170610180339145-0610_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170611090328\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170610%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170610180339145-0610_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170611090328&h=3fb57524&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b33906ceadc513f0485cf78a37b09f2c0f34ecb8","tid":288290,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170610/photo/bkn-20170610180339145-0610_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170611090328\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170610%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170610180339145-0610_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170611090328&h=67abdc0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170610/photo/bkn-20170610180339145-0610_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170611090328\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2F